::Striker::

Striker raises an eyebrow as he hears one of the Dinobot's order him to 
sniff. He does so. He was not a hunter, but he wasn't an idiot either. He 
picks up a female scent coming from the other bot.

He turns to her. "Allright, I believe its time for both of you to transform," 
he says firmly, "That's an order."
